source.name: 2005-2007 American Community Survey Three-Year PUMS Population File
source.description: National survey that collects data from a sample of the resident population in the United States. Housing units in every county in the United States and municipio in Puerto Rico, including institutional and non-institutional group quarters, are included in the sample.
